    "en": {
      "title": "Udarata begins the great feast",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Marking the beginning of the Udarata Esala Perahara festival, the planting of cups in the four major temples took place at the auspicious time of 03.03 in the morning today (29).",
        "Cups were planted in the four major temples namely Natha, Vishnu, Kataragama and Pattini, and since then, after conducting internal processions in the four major temples for five days, the Esala Perahara is scheduled to be visited on the streets."
      ],
